ay text-2xl\">PageCub</span></a><div class=\"hidden items-center gap-7 text-sm font-semibold text-ink/75 md:flex\"><a class=\"transition hover:text-ink\" href=\"/how-it-works\">How it works</a><a class=\"transition hover:text-ink\" href=\"/samples\">Samples</a><a class=\"transition hover:text-ink\" href=\"/pricing\">Pricing</a><a class=\"transition hover:text-ink\" href=\"/faq\">FAQ</a><a class=\"transition hover:text-ink\" href=\"/blog\">Blog</a></div><a class=\"inline-flex min-h-11 items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-ink px-5 py-2.5 text-sm font-bold text-white transition hover:-translate-y-0.5\" href=\"/create\">Start a Book</a></nav></header><header class=\"sticky top-0 z-50 border-b border-line/70 bg-cream/90 backdrop-blur\"><nav class=\"page-shell flex min-h-20 items-center justify-between gap-4\"><a class=\"flex items-center gap-3 font-bold text-ink\" aria-label=\"PageCub home\" href=\"/\"><span class=\"flex h-10 w-10 items-center justify-center rounded-2xl bg-honey text-ink shadow-sm\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-book-open h-5 w-5\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M12 7v14\"></path><path d=\"M3 18a1 1 0 0 1-1-1V4a1 1 0 0 1 1-1h5a4 4 0 0 1 4 4 4 4 0 0 1 4-4h5a1 1 0 0 1 1 1v13a1 1 0 0 1-1 1h-6a3 3 0 0 0-3 3 3 3 0 0 0-3-3z\"></path></svg></span><span class=\"display text-2xl\">PageCub</span></a><div class=\"hidden items-center gap-7 text-sm font-semibold text-ink/75 md:flex\"><a class=\"transition hover:text-ink\" href=\"/how-it-works\">How it works</a><a class=\"transition hover:text-ink\" href=\"/samples\">Samples</a><a class=\"transition hover:text-ink\" href=\"/pricing\">Pricing</a><a class=\"transition hover:text-ink\" href=\"/faq\">FAQ</a><a class=\"transition hover:text-ink\" href=\"/blog\">Blog</a></div><a class=\"inline-flex min-h-11 items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-ink px-5 py-2.5 text-sm font-bold text-white transition hover:-translate-y-0.5\" href=\"/create\">Start a Book</a></nav></header><main><section class=\"page-shell py-24\"><div class=\"max-w-2xl\"><p class=\"text-sm font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-sage mb-4\">About PageCub</p><h1 class=\"display text-5xl font-bold leading-tight mb-6\">Built for one child. Built for yours.</h1><p class=\"text-lg leading-8 text-ink/72\">PageCub is a personalized illustrated storybook service. You tell us about your child — who they are, what they love, what they&#x27;re going through — and we create a complete chapter book built around them, with real illustrations, a beginning, a heart, and an ending that fits.</p></div></section><section class=\"border-y border-line bg-card/70 py-16\"><div class=\"page-shell max-w-2xl\"><h2 class=\"display text-3xl font-bold mb-6\">About Aurelia</h2><p class=\"text-lg leading-9 text-ink/75\">You&#x27;ll notice most of our examples follow the same little girl, Aurelia. That&#x27;s my daughter. I originally built PageCub because I wanted to make her books — stories built around whatever she was going through, whatever she was into, whatever she couldn&#x27;t find on the shelf. She was the first reader. She still is.</p></div></section><section class=\"page-shell py-16 max-w-2xl\"><h2 class=\"display text-3xl font-bold mb-4\">How the books are made</h2><p class=\"text-ink/70 leading-7 mb-6\">When you submit the creation form, our system uses the details you provide — your child&#x27;s name, appearance, personality, world preferences, and the lesson you want the story to carry — to generate a complete 10-chapter illustrated storybook.</p><p class=\"text-ink/70 leading-7 mb-6\">The story and illustrations are generated by automated creative tools trained on children&#x27;s literature and illustration styles. No human author or illustrator reviews your specific book before delivery. What you receive is a finished, cohesive narrative with two full text pages and two illustrations per chapter — ready to read, save, or share.</p><p class=\"text-ink/70 leading-7 mb-6\">Every book includes a dedication page, opening note, and back matter with discussion questions and a draw-along prompt — all generated to match the tone and theme of your specific story.</p><p class=\"text-ink/70 leading-7\">You can choose from any illustration style in the creation form — watercolor, classic storybook, whimsical fantasy, cartoon, and more. The style you select shapes every illustration in the book consistently.</p></section><section class=\"bg-sage/10 py-16\"><div class=\"page-shell max-w-2xl\"><h2 class=\"display text-3xl font-bold mb-4\">What you get</h2><div class=\"rounded-2xl border border-line bg-card p-6 space-y-3 text-sm text-ink/75 leading-7\"><div class=\"flex items-start gap-3\"><span class=\"mt-1 h-2 w-2 rounded-full bg-honey flex-shrink-0\"></span><span>10-chapter personalized storybook</span></div><div class=\"flex items-start gap-3\"><span class=\"mt-1 h-2 w-2 rounded-full bg-honey flex-shrink-0\"></span><span>2 text pages + 2 illustrations per chapter (20 illustrations total)</span></div><div class=\"flex items-start gap-3\"><span class=\"mt-1 h-2 w-2 rounded-full bg-honey flex-shrink-0\"></span><span>Title page and cover</span></div><div class=\"flex items-start gap-3\"><span class=\"mt-1 h-2 w-2 rounded-full bg-honey flex-shrink-0\"></span><span>Dedication page</span></div><div class=\"flex items-start gap-3\"><span class=\"mt-1 h-2 w-2 rounded-full bg-honey flex-shrink-0\"></span><span>Opening note page</span></div><div class=\"flex items-start gap-3\"><span class=\"mt-1 h-2 w-2 rounded-full bg-honey flex-shrink-0\"></span><span>Back matter: what the hero learned, follow-up questions for conversation, draw-along prompt</span></div><div class=\"flex items-start gap-3\"><span class=\"mt-1 h-2 w-2 rounded-full bg-honey flex-shrink-0\"></span><span>Delivered as a high-quality PDF</span></div><div class=\"flex items-start gap-3\"><span class=\"mt-1 h-2 w-2 rounded-full bg-honey flex-shrink-0\"></span><span>Print fulfillment coming soon — hardcover, ~48 pages</span></div></div></div></section><section class=\"page-shell py-16 max-w-2xl\"><h2 class=\"display text-3xl font-bold mb-8\">How we handle your information</h2><div class=\"grid gap-5 sm:grid-cols-2\"><div class=\"rounded-2xl border border-line bg-card p-6\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-lock h-6 w-6 text-sage mb-4\"><rect width=\"18\" height=\"11\" x=\"3\" y=\"11\" rx=\"2\" ry=\"2\"></rect><path d=\"M7 11V7a5 5 0 0 1 10 0v4\"></path></svg><h3 class=\"font-bold mb-2\">Private by design</h3><p class=\"text-sm text-ink/65 leading-6\">Details you submit about your child are used only to create your book. They are not shared with advertisers, sold to data brokers, or used to build profiles.</p></div><div class=\"rounded-2xl border border-line bg-card p-6\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-eye-off h-6 w-6 text-sage mb-4\"><path d=\"M10.733 5.076a10.744 10.744 0 0 1 11.205 6.575 1 1 0 0 1 0 .696 10.747 10.747 0 0 1-1.444 2.49\"></path><path d=\"M14.084 14.158a3 3 0 0 1-4.242-4.242\"></path><path d=\"M17.479 17.499a10.75 10.75 0 0 1-15.417-5.151 1 1 0 0 1 0-.696 10.75 10.75 0 0 1 4.446-5.143\"></path><path d=\"m2 2 20 20\"></path></svg><h3 class=\"font-bold mb-2\">No data selling</h3><p class=\"text-sm text-ink/65 leading-6\">We do not sell, rent, or trade your personal information or your child&#x27;s information to any third party. Full stop.</p></div><div class=\"rounded-2xl border border-line bg-card p-6\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-shield-check h-6 w-6 text-sage mb-4\"><path d=\"M20 13c0 5-3.5 7.5-7.66 8.95a1 1 0 0 1-.67-.01C7.5 20.5 4 18 4 13V6a1 1 0 0 1 1-1c2 0 4.5-1.2 6.24-2.72a1.17 1.17 0 0 1 1.52 0C14.51 3.81 17 5 19 5a1 1 0 0 1 1 1z\"></path><path d=\"m9 12 2 2 4-4\"></path></svg><h3 class=\"font-bold mb-2\">Made with permission</h3><p class=\"text-sm text-ink/65 leading-6\">The creation form requires confirmation that you are the parent, guardian, or have explicit permission to create a book for the child described.</p></div><div class=\"rounded-2xl border border-line bg-card p-6\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-heart-handshake h-6 w-6 text-sage mb-4\"><path d=\"M19 14c1.49-1.46 3-3.21 3-5.5A5.5 5.5 0 0 0 16.5 3c-1.76 0-3 .5-4.5 2-1.5-1.5-2.74-2-4.5-2A5.5 5.5 0 0 0 2 8.5c0 2.3 1.5 4.05 3 5.5l7 7Z\"></path><path d=\"M12 5 9.04 7.96a2.17 2.17 0 0 0 0 3.08c.82.82 2.13.85 3 .07l2.07-1.9a2.82 2.82 0 0 1 3.79 0l2.96 2.66\"></path><path d=\"m18 15-2-2\"></path><path d=\"m15 18-2-2\"></path></svg><h3 class=\"font-bold mb-2\">You can request deletion</h3><p class=\"text-sm text-ink/65 leading-6\">If you want your data and your child&#x27;s details removed from our systems, email support@pagecub.com and we will honor that request.</p></div></div></section><section class=\"page-shell pb-16 max-w-2xl\"><h2 class=\"display text-3xl font-bold mb-4\">Questions?</h2><p class=\"text-ink/70 leading-7 mb-6\">Reach us at <a href=\"mailto:support@pagecub.com\" class=\"text-honey font-bold hover:underline\">support@pagecub.com</a>. We&#x27;re happy to answer questions about how the books are made, what data we hold, or anything else before you create.</p><a class=\"inline-flex min-h-12 items-center justify-center gap-2 rounded-full px-6 py-3 text-sm font-bold transition bg-honey text-ink shadow-button hover:-translate-y-0.5\" href=\"/create\">Start a Book<svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-arrow-right h-4 w-4\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M5 12h14\"></path><path d=\"m12 5 7 7-7 7\"></path></svg></a></section></main><footer class=\"border-t border-line bg-card/70\"><div class=\"page-shell grid gap-8 py-10 md:grid-cols-[1.2fr_2fr]\"><div><p class=\"display text-2xl font-bold\">PageCub</p><p class=\"mt-3 max-w-sm text-sm leading-6 text-ink/70\">Personalized illustrated storybooks for families, birthdays, milestones, and everyday bravery.</p><p class=\"mt-4 text-sm font-semibold text-ink/75\">Print fulfillment coming soon.</p></div><div class=\"flex flex-wrap gap-x-6 gap-y-3 text-sm font-semibold text-ink/70 md:justify-end\"><a class=\"hover:text-ink\" href=\"/samples\">Samples</a><a class=\"hover:text-ink\" href=\"/how-it-works\">How it works</a><a class=\"hover:text-ink\" href=\"/pricing\">Pricing</a><a class=\"hover:text-ink\" href=\"/faq\">FAQ</a><a class=\"hover:text-ink\" href=\"/about\">About &amp; safety</a><a class=\"hover:text-ink\" href=\"/privacy\">Privacy</a><a class=\"hover:text-ink\" href=\"/terms\">Terms</a></div></div></footer><footer class=\"border-t border-line bg-card/70\"><div class=\"page-shell grid gap-8 py-10 md:grid-cols-[1.2fr_2fr]\"><div><p class=\"display text-2xl font-bold\">PageCub</p><p class=\"mt-3 max-w-sm text-sm leading-6 text-ink/70\">Personalized illustrated storybooks for families, birthdays, milestones, and everyday bravery.</p><p class=\"mt-4 text-sm font-semibold text-ink/75\">Print fulfillment coming soon.</p></div><div class=\"flex flex-wrap gap-x-6 gap-y-3 text-sm fo